"Final Ranking Reward":
"About the Final Ranking Reward

At the end of the event, participating groups are ranked by their Total Points. You can then receive a \"Final Reward\" from Arkuma based on your ranking.

Once you have obtained your Stars, new prizes will be added to Arkuma's Prize Shop, which can be purchased for Stars.
